Noteworthy changes in version 0.2.0 (unreleased) [C0/A0/R3]
------------------------------------------------


 * Interface changes relative to version 0.1.2
   ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
   ntbtls_get_last_alert           NEW function.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.1.2 (2017-09-19) [C0/A0/R2]
------------------------------------------------

 * Add support for secp384r1, secp521r1, and 3 Brainpool curves.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.1.1 (2017-03-16) [C0/A0/R1]
------------------------------------------------

 * Now supports ECDHE-RSA key exchange.


Noteworthy changes in version 0.1.0 (2017-02-21) [C0/A0/R0]
------------------------------------------------

 * Initial experimental release with only the client code.


